<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gam ni banga vak chuh a um,
 Kumsawta vak zing chuh;
 Nitum um ngeiloh na mun chuh,
 A vak chuh Hukdampa.

[V2]
 Lungthim niem in Kross pu leng,
 Lallukhuk chuh khui tiu;
 Zie mun achun I chen tieng,
 Kumsawt vakna mun achun.

[V3]
 2. Gam a um hi, lungmuon na gam,
 Damsung tuipi galah;
 Buoina huihpi nun takloh na,
 Ziechun go khawl hitiu.

[V4]
 3. In a um hi, In lopi chuh,
 Van In nuom hawihtak chuh;
 Ziemuna I ngaihtak teu chun,
 Ei na lamtuoh un-au.

[V5]
 4. Khawvel gam hi taihsan I nuom,
 Chawmlo a bei ding hi;
 Van mithieng laia buol I nuom,
 Nawp tawp lohna gamah.</lyrics>
<title>THE BRIGHT FOR EVERMORE</title>
<hymn_number>390</hymn_number>
</song>